docs {
  ## List Departments
  แสดงรายการแผนกทั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Retrieves all departments configured in the business unit with pagination and search support.


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "code": "DEPT-001",
        "name": "Kitchen",
        "description": "Kitchen department",
        "is_active": true,
        "created_at": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "total": 100,
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 10
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}
